Chuck Norris Facts Fortune-Mod
Packaged By: Paul Kessler
FEb 2, 2006

DISCLAIMER!

Give credit where credit is due I'm just the guy that packaged up
all of these amazing facts about Chuck Norris. I repackaged the quotes
from the following website:

http://www.chucknorrisfacts.com/index.html

On the last page they also give credit to far to many people to list here
for providing many of these quotes. Please visit the site and enjoy!

INSTALL
	Copy the files chucknorris and chucknorris.dat into /usr/share/fortune/
	That is it.


The software package, including the files:
	chucknorris		(the quotes)
	chucknorris.dat		(the quotes index)
	README			(this file)


